snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listInstances Sample
snippets.description: Lists Instances in a given project and location.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager getInstance Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single instance.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager createInstance Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new instance in a given project and location.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listRepositories Sample
snippets.description: Lists Repositories in a given project and location. The instance field is required in the query parameter for requests using the securesourcemanager.googleapis.com endpoint.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager createRepository Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new repository in a given project and location. The Repository.Instance field is required in the request body for requests using the securesourcemanager.googleapis.com endpoint.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager updateRepository Sample
snippets.description: Updates the metadata of a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listHooks Sample
snippets.description: Lists hooks in a given repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager createHook Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new hook in a given repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager updateHook Sample
snippets.description: Updates the metadata of a hook.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager getIamPolicyRepo Sample
snippets.description: Get IAM policy for a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager setIamPolicyRepo Sample
snippets.description: Set IAM policy on a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager testIamPermissionsRepo Sample
snippets.description: Test IAM permissions on a repository. IAM permission checks are not required on this method.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager createBranchRule Sample
snippets.description: CreateBranchRule creates a branch rule in a given repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listBranchRules Sample
snippets.description: ListBranchRules lists branch rules in a given repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listPullRequests Sample
snippets.description: Lists pull requests in a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager closePullRequest Sample
snippets.description: Closes a pull request without merging.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager listPullRequestFileDiffs Sample
snippets.description: Lists a pull request's file diffs.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager fetchTree Sample
snippets.description: Fetches a tree from a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager fetchBlob Sample
snippets.description: Fetches a blob from a repository.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager createPullRequestComment Sample
snippets.description: Creates a pull request comment. This function is used to create a single PullRequestComment of type Comment, or a single PullRequestComment of type Code that's replying to another PullRequestComment of type Code. Use BatchCreatePullRequestComments to create multiple PullRequestComments for code reviews.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager batchCreatePullRequestComments Sample
snippets.description: Batch creates pull request comments. This function is used to create multiple PullRequestComments for code review. There needs to be exactly one PullRequestComment of type Review, and at most 100 PullRequestComments of type Code per request. The Postition of the code comments must be unique within the request.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager resolvePullRequestComments Sample
snippets.description: Resolves pull request comments. A list of PullRequestComment names must be provided. The PullRequestComment names must be in the same conversation thread. If auto_fill is set, all comments in the conversation thread will be resolved.

snippets.title: SecureSourceManager unresolvePullRequestComments Sample
snippets.description: Unresolves pull request comments. A list of PullRequestComment names must be provided. The PullRequestComment names must be in the same conversation thread. If auto_fill is set, all comments in the conversation thread will be unresolved.
